<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6825733>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Salmoneus shojaei sp. nov., holotype, ovigerous specimen (cl 5.33 mm) from Khamir Port, Iran (MNHN-IU-2014- 1257). (A) anterior part of carapace and left cephalic appendages, lateral view; (B) same, dorsal view; (C) pleon, lateral view; (D) telson and uropods, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6825733/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6825739>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Salmoneus shojaei sp. nov., holotype, ovigerous specimen (cl 5.33 mm) from Khamir Port, Iran (MNHN-IU-2014- 1257). (A) third maxilliped, ventro-lateral view; (B) second pereiopod, lateral view; (C) third pereiopod, lateral view; (D) fourth pereiopod, lateral view; (E) fifth pereiopod, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6825739/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6825735>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Salmoneus shojaei sp. nov., holotype, ovigerous specimen (cl 5.33 mm) from Khamir Port, Iran (MNHN-IU-2014- 1257). (A) major cheliped, lateral view; (B) same, distal portion of carpus and chela, lateral view; (C) same, mesial view; (D) minor cheliped, lateral view; (E) same, chela, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6825735/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6825741>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Salmoneus shojaei sp. nov., shrimps in life. (A) paratype, non-ovigerous specimen from Khamir Port, Iran (MNHN- IU-2014-1259); (B) paratype, non-ovigerous specimen from the same locality (FLMNH UF 60587). Photographs by Mr. Rashed Abdollahi." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6825741/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

